lineType.description:
Transaction line type.
Possible Values:
-&gt; Inventory = "GI";
-&gt; NonInventory = "GN";
-&gt; MiscCharge = "MI";
-&gt; Freight = "FR";
-&gt; Discount = "DS";
-&gt; Reallocation = "RA";

